This paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also proposes a novel training strategy using deep neural networks, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of datasets and their representation, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
